---

<BaseLayout title="The Tangle Protocol substrate" description="The protocol layer behind tangle.tools: operator network, staking, x402 settlement. The infrastructure substrate Blueprints run on.">

  <style>
    /* ═══ Backers strip. Replaces "Partners & Backers" generic label
       with a real eyebrow + h2 + lede framing, plus an edge-faded
       hover-pausable marquee. ═══ */
    .ov-partners {
      background: var(--depth-1, #0c0b1d);
      padding: 4.5rem 8% 4.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }
    .ov-partners-inner {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .ov-partners-head {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 52rem;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    }
    .ov-partners-eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: #818cf8;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .ov-partners-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display, system-ui);
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.4vw, 2.5rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-primary, #ffffff);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    }
    .ov-partners-lede {
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--text-secondary, rgba(244, 244, 249, 0.6));
      margin: 0;
    }
    .ov-partners-marquee {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%);
      mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%);
    }
    .ov-partners-track {
      display: flex;
      gap: 3.5rem;
      width: max-content;
      align-items: center;
      animation: ov-partners-scroll 50s linear infinite;
    }
    .ov-partners-marquee:hover .ov-partners-track {
      animation-play-state: paused;
    }
    @keyframes ov-partners-scroll {
      from { transform: translateX(0); }
      to   { transform: translateX(-33.3333%); }
    }
    .ov-partners-logo {
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      height: 38px;
      width: auto;
      max-width: 160px;
      object-fit: contain;
      filter: grayscale(1) brightness(1.4);
      opacity: 0.55;
      transition: filter 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
    }
    .ov-partners-logo:hover {
      filter: grayscale(0) brightness(1);
      opacity: 1;
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .ov-partners-track { animation: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .ov-partners { padding: 3.5rem 6%; }
      .ov-partners-logo { height: 30px; }
    }

    .ov-surfaces-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
    }
    @media (max-width: 1100px) {
      .ov-surfaces-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .ov-surfaces-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    /* HOW IT FLOWS. data-flow diagram */
    .dflow {
      position: relative;
      max-width: 64rem;
      margin: 3rem auto 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto 220px auto auto;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .dflow-cols {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .dflow-col {
      background: var(--depth-2);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 1rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      min-height: 14rem;
    }
    .dflow-col[data-source="public"] { border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.3); }
    .dflow-col[data-source="personal"] { border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.3); }
    .dflow-col[data-source="licensed"] { border-color: rgba(255,184,0,0.3); }
    .dflow-col-head { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.2rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(165,170,252,0.2); }
    .dflow-col-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; color: var(--brand-cool); }
    .dflow-col[data-source="personal"] .dflow-col-label { color: #34D399; }
    .dflow-col[data-source="licensed"] .dflow-col-label { color: #FFB800; }
    .dflow-col-sub { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
    .dflow-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .dflow-list li { padding-left: 0.85rem; position: relative; }
    .dflow-list li::before { content: '·'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--brand-cool); font-weight: 700; }
    .dflow-col-meta { margin-top: auto; padding-top: 0.6rem; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.04em; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle); }

    .dflow-svg {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      width: 100%;
      height: 220px;
      margin: -10px 0 -10px;
      pointer-events: none;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .dflow-beam {
      stroke-dashoffset: 800;
      animation: dflow-draw 1.6s cubic-bezier(0.6,0.05,0.4,1) forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }
    .dflow.is-in-view .dflow-beam {
      opacity: 1;
      animation-play-state: running;
    }
    .dflow-beam-out {
      animation-delay: 0.7s;
    }
    @keyframes dflow-draw {
      from { stroke-dashoffset: 800; opacity: 0; }
      to   { stroke-dashoffset: 0;   opacity: 1; }
    }

    .dflow-mid { display: flex; justify-content: center; }
    .dflow-window {
      width: min(100%, 38rem);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99,102,241,0.06), rgba(165,170,252,0.04));
      border: 1px solid rgba(99,102,241,0.3);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(99,102,241,0.1);
    }
    .dflow-window-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(165,170,252,0.22); }
    .dflow-window-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: #A5AAFC; }
    .dflow-window-meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .dflow-window-bars { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.55rem; }
    .dflow-window-bar { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 5rem 1fr 3rem; gap: 0.85rem; align-items: center; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    .dflow-window-bar-key { color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
    .dflow-window-bar-track { display: block; height: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; }
    .dflow-window-bar-track > span { display: block; height: 100%; border-radius: 3px; }
    .dflow-window-bar-num { color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 700; text-align: right; }

    .dflow-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
    .dflow-eval {
      width: min(100%, 36rem);
      background: var(--depth-2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.3);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .dflow-eval-head { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.85rem; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(52,211,153,0.22); }
    .dflow-eval-label { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: #34D399; }
    .dflow-eval-meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
    .dflow-eval-rows { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.55rem; }
    .dflow-eval-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 7rem 1fr 2.5rem; gap: 0.85rem; align-items: center; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    .dflow-eval-bar { display: block; height: 6px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-radius: 3px; overflow: hidden; }
    .dflow-eval-bar > span { display: block; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #34D399, #6EE7B7); border-radius: 3px; }
    .dflow-eval-num { color: #34D399; font-weight: 700; text-align: right; font-family: var(--font-mono); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .dflow-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .dflow-svg { display: none; }
      .dflow-mid { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .dflow-beam { animation: none !important; opacity: 1 !important; stroke-dashoffset: 0 !important; }
    }

    /* ─── Lifecycle (vault). request flow through the protocol ─── */
    .ov-life-section { position: relative; }
    .ov-life-head {
      max-width: 56rem;
      margin: 0 0 2.75rem;
    }
    .ov-life-eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.6875rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: #047857;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
    }
    .ov-life-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: var(--type-h2);
      font-weight: var(--type-h2-weight);
      line-height: var(--type-h2-line);
      letter-spacing: var(--type-h2-track);
      color: #191c24;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      text-wrap: balance;
      max-width: 38rem;
    }
    .ov-life-lede {
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #3a3a50;
      max-width: 48rem;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .ov-life-stage {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.18);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem 2rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.08), 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.6) inset;
    }
    .ov-life-svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }
    .ov-life-legend {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      gap: 0.875rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px dashed rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.22);
    }
    .ov-life-leg {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.8125rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: #3a3a50;
    }
    .ov-life-leg strong {
      color: #191c24;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .ov-life-leg code {
      background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.08);
      color: #191c24;
      padding: 0.05rem 0.35rem;
      border-radius: 3px;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }
    .ov-life-leg-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .ov-life-leg-dot--in       { background: #6366F1; }
    .ov-life-leg-dot--sandbox  { background: #4F46E5; }
    .ov-life-leg-dot--router   { background: #4338CA; }
    .ov-life-leg-dot--agent    { background: #7C3AED; }
    .ov-life-leg-dot--snap     { background: #2563EB; }
    .ov-life-leg-dot--ok       { background: #059669; }
    .ov-life-foot {
      margin-top: 1.75rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
    .ov-life-foot-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      color: #4F46E5;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.18s ease, transform 0.18s ease;
    }
    .ov-life-foot-link:hover {
      color: #3730A3;
      transform: translateX(2px);
    }
    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .ov-life-legend { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 0.875rem; }
      .ov-life-stage  { padding: 1.25rem 1rem; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .ov-life-legend { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .ov-life-svg circle[r="14"],
      .ov-life-svg circle[r="12"],
      .ov-life-svg circle[r="3.5"],
      .ov-life-svg circle[r="3"] { display: none; }
    }
  </style>

  <script>
    // Activate diagram beams when the section enters viewport.
    (() => {
      const flow = document.querySelector('.dflow');
      if (!flow) return;
      if (window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches) {
        flow.classList.add('is-in-view');
        return;
      }
      const io = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
        for (const e of entries) {
          if (e.isIntersecting) { flow.classList.add('is-in-view'); io.disconnect(); break; }
        }
      }, { threshold: 0.25 });
      io.observe(flow);
    })();
  </script>

  <Hero
    eyebrow="TANGLE PROTOCOL"
    eyebrowColor="brand"
    eyebrowIcon="shield"
    title={`One Blueprint.<br/>Many <span class="wf-gradient-text">operator instances.</span>`}
    subtitle="The crypto-economic substrate underneath every Blueprint: operator instancing, staking-backed SLAs, slashing, x402 settlement on every call."
    lede="Developers ship a Blueprint once. The protocol runs it on a network of staked operators, settles per-call payouts in any asset, and slashes operators that miss SLAs. No infra, no SLA, no on-call."
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Explore Docs', href: 'https://docs.tangle.tools', external: true }}
    secondaryCta={{ label: 'View Stake', href: '/stake' }}
    layout="one-col"
    align="left"
    videoBg={{
      poster: '/images/hero/abstract-objects-poster.jpg',
      webm: '/videos/abstract-objects.webm',
      mp4: '/videos/abstract-objects.mp4',
    }}
  />

  <StatsStrip
    items={[
      { label: '32+ Blueprints in production', icon: 'layers' },
      { label: '200+ operator instances running', icon: 'globe' },
      { label: 'Staking-backed SLAs', icon: 'shield' },
      { label: 'x402 settlement on every call', icon: 'dollar' },
    ]}
  />

  {/* Partners & backers strip. Proper section header with eyebrow +
      h2 + sub framing, replacing the bare "Partners & Backers" label
      that read as VC-list filler. Marquee retained but with edge-fade
      mask + hover-pause + tighter framing. */}
  <section class="ov-partners">
    <div class="ov-partners-inner">
      <div class="ov-partners-head">
        <div class="ov-partners-eyebrow">BACKED BY</div>
        <h2 class="ov-partners-title">The funds + builders financing AI infrastructure.</h2>
        <p class="ov-partners-lede">Operators serving production Blueprints, restaking partners securing the substrate, and the funds that wrote the cheques.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ov-partners-marquee">
        <div class="ov-partners-track">
          {[...partnerLogos, ...partnerLogos, ...partnerLogos].map(({ name, src }) => (
            <img src={src} alt={name} loading="lazy" class="ov-partners-logo" />
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section: Request lifecycle (vault). animated horizontal substrate diagram -->
  <Section variant="vault" pad="default" maxWidth="wide" class="ov-life-section">
    <div class="ov-life-head">
