      <h2 class="ov-life-title">How a request flows through the protocol.</h2>
      <p class="ov-life-lede">Every Blueprint call moves through the same path: input arrives at the router, a sandboxed operator instance picks it up, the model runs against your tools, the snapshot lands, and the protocol settles the bill in the asset you priced it in.</p>
    </div>

